### Event Information: Hack In The Box (HITB)

**Event Title:** EVT - HackInTheBox  
**Organizers:** D4rkm4tter & Kampf  
**Description:** Hack In The Box is an evening hacker space that allows attendees to gather after-hours during SAINTCON. It runs after the main speaking tracks and offers accommodations for soldering, presentations, networking, and collaboration on contests. HITB has been held since 2016 and operates as a safe space for community interaction.  

**Location:** Near the event venue of SAINTCON  
**Hours of Operation:**  
- **Tuesday:** 6:00 PM - 11:59 PM  
- **Wednesday:** 6:00 PM - 11:59 PM  
- **Thursday:** 6:00 PM - 11:59 PM  

**Links:**  
- **Event Page:** [HackInTheBox](https://saintcon.org/evt-hackinthebox/)  
